{"tid":1632524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手裝修 大家討論下呢個方法可唔可行","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:51:05.000Z","uid":212884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65ab5f310217c6cb1e2a4a2dd084ee67defde04f","tid":1632524,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:21:47.000Z","msg":"由蟲系魔法師嘅方向諗<br />\n<br />\n蟲可能大家都覺得核突 所以唔敢做呢個系嘅魔法師<br />\n<br />\n但用自然方法吸引蟲 大家又點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">材料：<br />\n1）砂糖<br />\n2）鹽<br />\n3）水<br />\n4）臭雞蛋<br />\n5）膠水樽<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">製造方法：<br />\n1）將砂糖同鹽（比例1:1）倒入膠水樽<br />\n2）入小小水<br />\n3）倒臭雞蛋<br />\n4）用保鮮紙包實<br />\n5）入場倒幾枝入裝修工程入面</span><br />\n<br />\n呢招低成本無毒化武好處係<br />\n<br />\n就算比狗周到材料都唔會出事 又可以現場即整<br />\n<br />\n而且對要裝修嘅舖 唔係另一日封塊木板抹下個舖面就做到生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我未試 但大家覺得可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366729a38eb137d3b471b2ae8a90eb685d4962c7","tid":1632524,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:36:20.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ddacf1b93e0f90a855b0d2406dedaba377fb7b0e","tid":1632524,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:36:30.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5fe38ab770368cae11173179a6540788a27184df","tid":1632524,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:36:42.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ce703d199e471392e8aa142da82a529bf8b4682b","tid":1632524,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:36:53.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7e76536bd6fc8f9a6f22baef76eb0cbfff32c239","tid":1632524,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:37:20.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"767a41116d13ce339219b33c98